platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Everyone needs a task manager—and Things is adaptable enough for anyone. This Apple Design Award winner is crisp and lightweight, featuring a simple but effective interface. The ever-present Magic Plus button makes it easy to add to-dos from anywhere in the app, and organizing items is as simple as dragging them where you want them. It’s like the unicorn of productivity tools: deep enough for serious work, surprisingly easy to use, and gorgeous enough to enjoy staring at.
人人都需要一款任務管理工具，而這款 Apple Design Award 得獎 App 則能靈活配合各人所需。整理項目非常簡單，只需將其拖移至所需位置即可。使用「神奇加號」按鈕，即可輕鬆地在 App 內任何位置新增待辦事項。
明明感觉很忙，却又不知道在忙什么，你也许只是需要一个任务管理器。这款 Apple 设计大奖获奖作品拥有用户友好的界面设计，管理项目简单易上手。Magic Plus 按钮让你可以在任意位置快捷添加待办事项。

Everyone needs a task manager – and this Apple Design Award winner is adaptable enough for anyone. Organising items is as simple as dragging them where you want them, and the Magic Plus button makes it easy to add to-dos from anywhere in the app.
タスク管理のツールは誰もが必要としていますが、Apple Design Awardを受賞したこのアプリは、多彩なニーズに柔軟に対応しています。思い通りの場所にドラッグするだけで項目を整理でき、「+」ボタンを使えば、アプリのどこからでもTo Doを簡単に追加できます。

Everyone needs a task manager—and Things is adaptable enough for anyone. This Apple Design Award winner is crisp and lightweight, featuring a simple but effective interface. The ever-present Magic Plus button makes it easy to add to-do’s from anywhere in the app, and organising items is as simple as dragging them where you want them. It’s like the unicorn of productivity tools: deep enough for serious work, surprisingly easy to use, and gorgeous enough to enjoy staring at.
這款 Apple 設計大獎得主是你理想的任務管理工具。你可以輕鬆拖曳項目來重新安排順序，並使用 Magic Plus 按鈕快速新增待辦事項，提升作業效率。

Tout le monde a besoin d’un gestionnaire de tâches : cette app lauréate d’un Apple Design Award s’adapte justement à tous les profils. Organisez simplement des éléments en les faisant glisser où vous le souhaitez, tandis que le bouton Magic Plus vous permet d’ajouter facilement des listes de tâches depuis n’importe quelle page de l’app.
